sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Data Scientist
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Experiment API Request (with Kubernetes Auth)
    Client->>Proxy: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Proxy->>MLflow: Forward request<br/>x-remote-user + x-remote-groups headers
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>mlflow.kubeflow.org/experiments<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allowed/Denied
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run record<br/>Auth: Username/password
    PG-->>MLflow: OK
    MLflow-->>Client: JSON Response (run metadata)

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Artifact Upload
    Client->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allowed
    MLflow->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / Access Key<br/>TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflow: 200 OK
    MLflow-->>Client: Artifact logged

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion
    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry SDK
    OTel->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces (protobuf)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>X-MLFLOW-EXPERIMENT-ID header
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>mlflow.kubeflow.org/experiments
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Allowed
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT trace data
    PG-->>MLflow: OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Workspace Listing
    Client->>MLflow: GET /api/2.0/mlflow/workspaces/list<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(per namespace)
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Namespace access list
    MLflow-->>Client: Filtered workspace list
